These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  pilot, scientist, social-worker, chef, dancer, dressmaker, photographer
7 different games are played: go, whist, poker, bridge, mah-jongg, domino, billiard
 1. the person playing go is the scientist##1
 2. the dressmaker is on the right of the dancer##1
 3. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
 4. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 5. the person playing go is the scientist##1
 6. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 7. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the chef is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 9. the pilot is on the left of the social-worker##1
10. the dancer is the person playing domino##1
11. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
12. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
13. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
14. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
15. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
16. the chef is the person playing whist##1
17. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
18. the person playing go is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |     6     |      7      |
| Job    | photographer    | dancer  | dressmaker       | scientist | pilot | social-worker | chef        |
| Game   | mah-jongg | domino | poker | go    | billiard   | bridge   | whist |

