.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: satire, martial-arts, animation, crime, horror, zombie, romance
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, canadian, russian, polish, chinese, dutch, indian
 1. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the russian##3
 3. the russian is in an odd position##4
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the canadian##1
 5. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
 6. the polish is in an odd position##4
 7. the indian is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the indian is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
10. the dutch is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the indian is on the left of the dutch##1
12. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
13. the chinese is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
14. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the russian##3
15. the person watching animation movies is the canadian##1
16. the canadian is the person watching animation movies##1
17. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |    3    |    4    |       5       |     6     |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts    | satire | zombie     | horror | animation | romance     | crime |
| Nationality       | indian | dutch      | russian | chinese  | canadian      | nigerian | polish   |

