.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, reggae, indie, blues, folk, country, classical
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour, skiing, rugby, skateboarding, lacrosse, golf
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is the fan of reggae##1
 2. the fan of country is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is skiing and the fan of classical##2
 4. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 7. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's sport is skiing##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the fan of blues##1
13. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the fan of indie##5
14. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
15. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |       3       |     4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
| Music-Genre       | classical | indie | folk | country | blues | electronic | reggae |
| Sport   | golf   | skateboarding    | skiing     | lacrosse      | biathlon     | rugby   | parkour    |

