.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-4::.
There 7 different types of food: lettuce, corn, tomato, zucchini, cucumber, banana, peas
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, game, dannemann, havana, davidoff, aristoff, swisher
 1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
 3. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
 4. the game-smoker is the person eating peas##1
 5. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
 6. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5
 9. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the havana-smoker##5
10. the davidoff-smoker is between the person eating lettuce and the person eating corn##2
11. the game-smoker is on the right of the person eating banana##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
13. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5
14. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
15. the havana-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
16. the game-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |   5    |   6    |   7   |
| Food   | banana | peas    | zucchini | tomato | lettuce | cucumber    | corn |
| Cigar           | swisher       | game | ritmeester   | dannemann    | aristoff    | davidoff | havana |

