 3. the italian is in an odd position##4
 4. the indian is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is the russian##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
 8. the american is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 9. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
10. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
11. the mexican is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
12. the person who's birthday is in april is between the american and the person who's birthday is in september##2
13. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
14. the person who's birthday is in december is between the mexican and the person who's birthday is in august##2
15. the american is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
