.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-17::.
7 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, rat, lizard, fish, dog, frog
7 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, poker, backgammon, monopoly, bridge, domino
 1. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
 2. the person playing domino is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 5. the person playing bridge is the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person playing poker is the owner of the frog##1
 7. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
10. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
11. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
12. the owner of the ferret is the person playing domino##1
13. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4      |        5        |      6      |       7       |
| Pet   | lizard     | rat   | fish | dog     | ferret           | frog         | horse |
| Game        | bridge | monopoly | mah-jongg | scrabble | domino | poker | backgammon     |

